data.description: This beautiful home is located on 1.5 acres in the quiet neighborhood of Alpine Country Club Estates. The 2,112 sq.ft. home has a semi open layout, with tons of natural light. The sequestered master has a spa like en suite with walk in shower and soaker tub. The main part of the house has wood look floors and a spaciously homey feel. There are also 2 bedrooms with a Jack & Jill style bathroom as well as an office and formal dining room. Outside, you will find AMAZING views and plenty of privacy.
